caption: The @naacp has unveiled its new #KeepAdvancing campaign, a bold approach to driving civic engagement and Black equity. Designed to reignite the movement for social justice, this campaign draws momentum from the power of Blackout Tuesday,  We are proud to have served as the creative partner for this campaign, working alongside @eleanor.films, the first and only Black woman-owned production company in the U.S. and the UK, to bring the work to life.
